%html
  %head
    %title Movie
    = stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true
    = javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true
    = csrf_meta_tags
  %body
    = render 'layouts/nav'
    .container
      = render 'layouts/flash'
      = yield
      .jumbotron
        %h1 Welcome to demo app
        %p
          In today's world internet is the most popular way of connecting with the people. At
          %a{:href => "http://www.tutorialrepublic.com", :target => "_blank"} tutorialrepublic.com
          you will learn the essential of web development technologies along with real life practice example, so that you can create your own website to connect with the people around the world.
        %p
          %a.btn.btn-success.btn-lg{:href => "http://www.tutorialrepublic.com", :target => "_blank"} Get started today
      .row
        .col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-2
          %h2 HTML
          %p HTML is a markup language that is used for creating web pages. The HTML tutorial section will help you understand the basics of HTML, so that you can create your own web pages or website.
          %p
            %a.btn.btn-success{:href => "http://www.tutorialrepublic.com/html-tutorial/", :target => "_blank"} Learn More »
        .col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-2
          %h2 CSS
          %p CSS is used for describing the presentation of web pages. The CSS tutorial section will help you learn the essentials of CSS, so that you can fine control the style and layout of your HTML document.
          %p
            %a.btn.btn-success{:href => "http://www.tutorialrepublic.com/css-tutorial/", :target => "_blank"} Learn More »
        .clearfix.visible-sm-block
        .col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-2
          %h2 Bootstrap
          %p Bootstrap is a powerful front-end framework for faster and easier web development. The Bootstrap tutorial section will help you learn the techniques of Bootstrap so that you can create web your own website with much less efforts.
          %p
            %a.btn.btn-success{:href => "http://www.tutorialrepublic.com/twitter-bootstrap-tutorial/", :target => "_blank"} Learn More »
        .clearfix.visible-md-block
        .col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-2
          %h2 References
          %p The references section outlines all the standard HTML tags and CSS properties along with other useful references such as color names and values, symbols and character entities, web safe fonts, language codes, HTTP messages and much more.
          %p
            %a.btn.btn-success{:href => "http://www.tutorialrepublic.com/twitter-bootstrap-tutorial/", :target => "_blank"} Learn More »
        .clearfix.visible-sm-block
        .col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-2
          %h2 Examples
          %p The examples section encloses an extensive collection of examples on various topic that you can try and test yourself using online HTML editor.
          %p
            %a.btn.btn-success{:href => "http://www.tutorialrepublic.com/twitter-bootstrap-tutorial/", :target => "_blank"} Learn More »
        .col-sm-6.col-md-4.col-lg-2
          %h2 FAQ
          %p The collection of Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) provides brief answers to many common questions related to web design and development.
          %p
            %a.btn.btn-success{:href => "http://www.tutorialrepublic.com/twitter-bootstrap-tutorial/", :target => "_blank"} Learn More »
      %hr/
      .row
        .col-sm-12
          %footer
            %p © Copyright 2015